## ğŸ“Š Project Overview

This project features a Power BI dashboard that provides an in-depth analysis of pizza sales data for a fictional pizza chain. The dashboard highlights key business metrics such as total sales, order volumes, best-selling pizzas, category performance, and time-based trends to support strategic decision-making.

---

## ğŸ¯ Business Objectives

- Identify high-performing and underperforming pizzas
- Analyze ordering behavior by weekday and time of day
- Understand customer preferences by category and size
- Monitor core KPIs including total sales, total orders, and AOV
- Enable data-driven marketing and operational strategies

